    type: string
  Line 10 (e) Cost (or other basis):
    type: string
  Line 10 (g) Adjustments to gain or loss:
    type: string
  Line 10 (h) Gain or (loss):
    type: string
  ? Line 11 — Gain from Form 4797 Part I; long-term gain from Forms 2439 and 6252; and long-term gain
    or (loss) from Forms 4684, 6781, and 8824
  : type: string
  Line 12 — Net long-term gain or (loss) from partnerships, S corporations, estates, and trusts (Schedule(s) K-1):
    type: string
  Line 13 — Capital gain distributions:
    type: string
  Line 14 — Long-term capital loss carryover:
    type: string
  Line 15 — Net long-term capital gain or (loss):
    type: string
  Line 16 — Combined net capital gain or (loss) (lines 7 + 15):
    type: string
  Line 17 — Are lines 15 and 16 both gains? — Yes:
    type: bool
  Line 17 — Are lines 15 and 16 both gains? — No:
    type: bool
  Line 18 — 28% Rate Gain Worksheet amount:
    type: string
  Line 19 — Unrecaptured Section 1250 Gain Worksheet amount:
    type: string
